{
  "stem": "1496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were 700-- eventually, there were 700 men and 300 women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we all lived in similar barracks, like in Krakau-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was even a better help available in-- in Schindler's factory, when something was wrong, you didn't-- you were not afraid to go in and get help.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was also a Jewish doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was nurses-- there were nurses, Jewish doctor, and they help as much as-- as possible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as far as I know, nobody really died in Schindler's factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were heated, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Minimum, but they were heated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- you know, he had few confidants what he really worked with, because you have to remember that he was a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He could not go out and buy the food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could not go out and sell the pots and pans on the black market.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was all done between Jewish confidants and other Polish people, how the business was conducted, because nobody would-- would do any business, actually, with Schindler himself.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was the beneficiary of all these-- all those transaction.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In addition, he was giving-- a lot of people were bribing-- tried to bribe him, in order to get to his factory, too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this we know only by-- I didn't-- I can't tell you that I witness anybody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we know about it, we've heard about it, that some people which were through-- again, through contact with confidants, were trying to get into the factory and buy theirself in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, through-- again, the Jewish-- Jewish policeman, the kapos, they had contact, and they were giving them the money and then somehow money or jewelry, you know, how Schindler had a lot jewelry, because he needed this also for bribing.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
